relatedNodes.html: “Colorado needs an Attorney General who will prioritize public safety over politics. I will work to protect your family like they were my own. As Attorney General, I will always stand up to those who threaten our safety, our environment, or our businesses.”

John Kellner is driven by service. His family legacy led him to the military. Law school brought him to Boulder. As a longtime prosecutor, he’ll bring his experience to fight back the crime wave and protect all Coloradans.
A Safer Colorado Begins with

Colorado’s violent crime rate is at a 25 year high. And at roughly 50%, Colorado’s prison recidivism rates are some of the worst in the country. We need an Attorney General ready to tackle this challenge.
John has taken on the drug cartels peddling poison in our communities, seizing hundreds of thousands of deadly fentanyl pills destined for our streets.
Colorado’s law enforcement put their lives on the line to protect us every day and they deserve to know we support them.
